casebody.head_matter:
Kirby GARDNER, Petitioner,
v.
Lorie DAVIS, Director, Texas Department of Criminal Justice, Correctional Institutions Division.
No. 18-9119
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
